export default () => `
Why did you create such a platform? +
Because this industry has been through enough forceful hoops that it was time that they were able to have a platform as stress-free as possible
What does one need to sign up? +
You will need an email and an account on the banking app we use.
When I sign up, do I have to sell or buy things? +
No, it is not mandatory to do either
Why do you require one banking app? +
To make it easier for not only us but vendor and buyer
Are you only able to view knives and guns? +
For right now, yes. This could change in the future
`;
